des: "This recipe is super simple to prepare. The result is great! anyone can make it. I'm sure you will be surprised! It tastes fantastic! Yummmmm!"
ins:
Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C).
Dissolve sugar in water. Beat in eggs.
Divide into tartlet shells and bake at 400 degrees F (200 degrees C) for 20 minutes.
